      <title>致立法者的信称越南议会将就“人事问题”举行会议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-parliament-meet-over-personnel-issues-says-letter-legislators-2024-03-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社看到的一封发给立法者的信显示，越南议会将于周四开会讨论未具体说明的“人事问题”，外界猜测越南最高领导层将进行改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-parliament-meet-over-personnel-issues-says-letter-legislators-2024-03-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 16:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的肖尔茨表示，拉法的袭击将使地区和平“非常困难”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/germanys-scholz-say-rafah-assault-would-make-regional-peace-very-difficult-2024-03-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周日在与约旦国王阿卜杜拉会谈后表示，以色列对加沙城市拉法的袭击将造成大量平民伤亡，这将使地区和平“非常困难”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/germanys-scholz-say-rafah-assault-would-make-regional-peace-very-difficult-2024-03-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 11:45:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿富汗客车、加油车相撞事故造成21人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/crash-involving-passenger-bus-fuel-truck-kills-21-afghanistan-2024-03-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗南部省政府称，周日发生的一起交通事故造成 21 人死亡、数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/crash-involving-passenger-bus-fuel-truck-kills-21-afghanistan-2024-03-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤与长期伴侣结婚</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-foreign-minister-penny-wong-marries-longtime-partner-2024-03-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤 (Penny Wong) 周日表示，她是该国第一位公开同性恋身份的女议员，已与她的伴侣苏菲·阿卢阿什 (Sophie Allouache) 结婚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-foreign-minister-penny-wong-marries-longtime-partner-2024-03-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 03:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚北部为热带气旋梅根做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-north-braces-tropical-cyclone-megan-2024-03-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，澳大利亚北领地和昆士兰州部分地区的居民被敦促为预计将在未来几天登陆的热带气旋做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-north-braces-tropical-cyclone-megan-2024-03-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 01:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>军方称，阿富汗边境附近的巴基斯坦军队哨所遇袭，造成 7 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/attack-pakistan-military-post-kills-5-security-force-members-military-says-2024-03-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦军方称，周六早些时候，武装分子使用一辆载有炸药和自杀式炸弹的车辆袭击了阿富汗附近巴基斯坦的一个军事哨所，造成七名安全部队成员死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/attack-pakistan-military-post-kills-5-security-force-members-military-says-2024-03-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 09:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行称谷歌第二次错误引用汇率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/malaysia-central-bank-says-google-misquoted-exchange-rate-second-time-2024-03-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行周六表示，谷歌错误引用了林吉特汇率，低估了林吉特兑美元汇率，并将寻求这家科技巨头的解释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/malaysia-central-bank-says-google-misquoted-exchange-rate-second-time-2024-03-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 08:47:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“立即掉头”：紧张局势升级之际，台湾再次警告中国海警船离开</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/turn-around-immediately-taiwan-warns-off-chinese-coast-guard-boats-again-2024-03-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于敏感的台湾海峡局势紧张，台湾周六连续第二天对进入靠近中国前线岛屿的限制水域的中国海警船只发出警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/turn-around-immediately-taiwan-warns-off-chinese-coast-guard-boats-again-2024-03-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 07:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据澳大利亚卫报报道，斐济维护中国警务协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fiji-upholds-china-policing-agreement-guardian-australia-reports-2024-03-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据澳大利亚《卫报》新闻网站报道，在对引起澳大利亚担忧的协议进行审查后，斐济将维持与中国的警务合作协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fiji-upholds-china-policing-agreement-guardian-australia-reports-2024-03-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 05:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>12名冲击香港立法会的人被判最高7年监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/twelve-sentenced-jail-storming-hong-kong-legislature-2019-2024-03-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，香港一家法院对一起备受瞩目的骚乱案判处 12 人监禁，刑期从四年多到近七年不等，该案与 2019 年一场支持民主的抗议活动中冲击香港立法机关有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/twelve-sentenced-jail-storming-hong-kong-legislature-2019-2024-03-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 03:39:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
